            <h3>About Us</h3><br>
            <p>Turning Point Trust is a not-for-profit organisation in New Zealand helping Kiwis in need. We provide tailor-made food boxes that includes breakfast, dinner and snacks to last at least a week. You can either donate food to our charity, donate a box or through monetary donations. We then pack the food boxes based on the family's needs.</p>
            <h4>Why donate to our charity?</h4>
            <p>Every day thousands of families are struggling across the Waikato and we want to help by providing immediate relief through food boxes. However, unlike other charities we donâ€™t want to just put a band-aid on the problem. We want to identify the root causes of why a family needed a food box in the first place. This way we deliver long term solutions through budgeting advice, help getting employment, getting a driver's licence or anything else a family might need to turn their lives around.</p>
            <p>With Turning Point Trust, you can be assured that your donations will go to people in your community that needs it the most. We believe in giving people a hand up rather than a hand out.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12"> 
            <blockquote>
                <p>"We aim to provide immediate relief to local families in need. With the focus to deliver long term solutions in the community."</p>
                <footer>Our Mission</footer>
            </blockquote>   
